Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Chernobyl and the Star Wars defence program
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yg2gd
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 14 Sep 1990
The lessons learned from Chernobyl, the hesitation in Congress over the Star Wars defence program, and the motivations of American doctors conducting clinical trials abroad.